>\n<br />\np.s 我都諗唔到點樣處理retaker問題，可能真係要被犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"一早封關咪冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3ba59466f3a33720f6d433f9baa6e26ea568a6","tid":1962470,"uid":61914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"睇你將考生安全定係考生所關心既考試成績擺係top priority<br />\n我諗英國取消考試都會畀考生屌撚到仆街<br />\n但人地為咗安全都會敢冒住被人剷到仆街既風險，照樣取消考試<br />\n唔通人地外國啲封城令搞到所有經濟活動停哂，唔會被人屌咩，affected parties仲多啦<br />\n做政客咁易被個輿情搞到自己唔識得分輕重既話，咁不如唔好做"},{"pid":"d71076bfd589a49ba11fe1d7545318ae7d3339e7","tid":1962470,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49fa81741752f51c05ee1c7f3a1914966bd7c538","tid":1962470,"uid":269763,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"無論最尾個方排係點，慘既只會係學生，唔會係政府<br />\n<br />\n政府唔係受害者，慘啲乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"係<br />\nretaker用大學入學試黎解決值唔值得諗?"},{"pid":"9d18177a4b5530083e7dc21687f9c5cff0b854ac","tid":1962470,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:26:06.000Z","msg":"用學校成績判別DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪傻，根本完全唔公平<br />\n<br />\nBand 3考第一比唔比佢入醫科？<br />\n<br />\n唔比=歧視，更何況人哋可能真係狀元<br />\n比=全香港所有校內考第一都可以讀醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}